        <body>
            <div xml:id="ed__aratus_latinus__al_4">
                <head>
                    <title>
                        <app>
                            <lem>Descriptio duorum semisspherium</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#P"> </rdg>
                        </app>
                    </title>
                </head>
                <p>Habet autem pondere totum medio terrae terrenum. differt 
                    <app>
                        <lem>enim</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">autem</rdg>
                    </app> per totum caelum seu terram aculeo suo quod 
                    <app>
                        <lem>in</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Pa"></rdg>
                    </app> circuitu habet et diuidit 
                    <app>
                        <lem>mediam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">medium</rdg>
                    </app> 
                    quoniam
                    <app>
                        <lem>terram</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Pa">terra</rdg>
                    </app> pertundit sicut per latera axis terrae aequaliter
                    <app> 
                        <lem>illam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Pa">illa</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#B">illum</rdg>
                    </app> habet et 
                    <app>
                        <lem></lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">aequaliter</rdg>
                    </app> ab eo 
                    <app>
                        <lem>ponderatam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Pa">ponderam</rdg>
                    </app>. aequalem enim ex utraque parte illam facit ipse medio 
                    <app>
                        <lem></lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Pa">loco</rdg>
                    </app> constans et in duo
                    <app>
                        <lem>eam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">eum</rdg>
                    </app> diuidens aut inponderatam ubique aequalem
                    <app>
                        <lem></lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">enim</rdg>
                    </app> et similem et ipsa 
                    <app>
                        <lem>enim</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B"></rdg>
                    </app> est in modum spherae  
                    <app>
                        <lem>seu</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Pa">ceu</rdg>
                    </app> et caelum ita et terra sicuti primis quidem 
                    <app>
                        <lem>facta aequam eam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">facti quia meam</rdg>
                    </app> caelo stellantia ut iam per omnia uel 
                    <app>
                        <lem>et</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #Pa">ut</rdg>
                    </app> per circuitum simili modo 
                    <app>
                        <lem> </lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">sperae</rdg>
                    </app> pondere 
                    <app>
                        <lem>aequalem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Pa">equale</rdg>
                    </app> per spatium sicut semisspheriis. quantum enim a terra habet altitudinem hoc semispherium tantum habet quod subtus terra 
                    <app>
                        <lem>longitudinem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Pa #B">longitudine</rdg>
                    </app>. aliud semispherium ipsa enim in medio 
                    <app>
                        <lem>iacet</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">ita et</rdg>
                    </app> duobus semispheriis.
